title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 2 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 2 2022
description:
Texas Governor Greg Abbott joins Clay to discuss Biden's authoritarian speech, the effect of busing illegal immigrants to "sanctuary cities" and how violations of Texas' border are violations of everyone's borders? Biden says Trump supporters not a threat to country after speech blasting "MAGA Republicans." Biden said in Thursday speech that Trump and "MAGA Republicans" dominating the Republican Party is "a threat to this country." Karine Jean-Pierre is an election denier. Senate candidate Herschel Walker talks with Clay to break down Biden's fascistic speech, radical far-left policies of his opponent Raphael Warnock, and how we need to bring people together.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
